*Hitno* je da se situacija promeni. (It is urgent that the situation changes.)
Svi znaju da je *hitno* da se pridržavamo novih pravila. (Everyone knows it is urgent to adhere to the new rules.)
Molim vas, *hitno* potrebna pomoć! (Please, urgent help needed!)
Postoje *hitne* situacije koje zahtevaju hitan odgovor. (There are urgent situations that require an immediate response.)
*Hitno* smo tražili naše stvari. (We urgently looked for our things.)